description	"Modified B2 Super Battle Droid

Class: SBD.
Class Summary:
A heavily modified advanced Super Battle Droid with tougher armor, that can engage in melee and ranged combat.

Weaponry:
- Arm Blaster + Arm Cannon 
(toggle via gun mode / lightsaber style control)
- Heavy Melee

Attributes:
- Firepower (3)
- Magnetic Plating
- Cortosis Armor
- Blast Armor
- Advanced Logic (2)
- Shield Recharge (1)
--- Advanced Electronics
- Can continue firing at a reduced rate while pulsed
--- Reactive Servos
- Only Strength (3) level characters and upwards can cause melee knockdowns
--- Prototype Force Shield
- Cannot be targeted by force powers

Abilities:
- Recharge (3) [Class Special 1]
- Radar (Enter recharge mode to reveal enemies on radar screen)
- Advanced Targeting [Class Special 2]

This heavily modified B2 series has tougher armor, faster rates of fire and is capable of both fighting Jedi and blaster troops with little difficulty."